Additional Middle Budget Activities
===================================

| --- | --- |
| Wild Wadi Water Park, Dubai | ~$68 |

Additional Low & Middle Budget Restaurants
==========================================

| Place | Average Check | Famous Dish |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Bu Qtair, Dubai | ~$12 | Grilled Fish |
| Karak House, Dubai | ~$10 | Karak Chai |
| Al Safadi, Dubai | ~$15 | Hummus |
| Al Dhafra, Abu Dhabi | ~$20 | Grilled Hammour |
| Bait El Khetyar, Abu Dhabi | ~$12 | Mandi |
| Shawarma Time, Abu Dhabi | ~$6 | Shawarma |

With these additional options for middle-budget activities and low & middle budget restaurants, you'll have more choices for an enjoyable trip in Dubai and Abu Dhabi. Have a great time!
